- \( d = 500 \, \text{mm} = 0.5 \, \text{m} \)

공식에 대입하면:

\[ V_u = \frac{0.25 \cdot 0.3 \cdot 0.5 \cdot \sqrt{24}}{1} \]

\[ \sqrt{24} \approx 4.899 \]

따라서,

\[ V_u = 0.25 \cdot 0.3 \cdot 0.5 \cdot 4.899 \]

계산하면:

